6. University of Southern Denmark, 7. Tampere University,", "8. University of Iceland, 9. Kyoto University, 10. Oslo Metropolitan University, 11. University of Kentucky", "The INORMS Research Evaluation Working Group (REWG) was established at the 2018 INORMS Congress to", "consider how best to ensure that research evaluation is meaningful, responsible and effective. To this end, group", "members representing the research management societies that make up INORMS have focussed on two main", "work-packages. The first seeks to draw attention to the burgeoning influence of World University Rankings on the", "behaviours of universities, by developing a methodology for 'rating' the Rankers in order to highlight some of their", "deficiencies and encourage better practices. The second has developed a five-stage process for evaluating", "responsibly called \u2018SCOPE\u2019, alongside a series of five arguments to persuade senior university leaders to adopt", "such responsible evaluation approaches. The outcomes of both workpackages will be presented at this", "workshop, providing perspectives from the global range of INORMS REWG members.", "8th International Network of Research Management Societies (INORMS) \u00a9"], "bbox": [[0.081704, 0.079488, 0.759428, 0.019902], [0.081704, 0.100866, 0.409114, 0.019902], [0.084267, 0.150497, 0.790456, 0.016039], [0.416923, 0.168209, -0.005609999999999948, 0.016039], [0.084267, 0.18626, 0.194664, 0.016039], [0.081704, 0.221825, 0.8452350000000001, 0.011941], [0.081704, 0.234652, 0.845205, 0.011941], [0.081704, 0.247479, 0.693529, 0.011941], [0.084267, 0.287959, 0.826608, 0.013268], [0.081704, 0.305774, 0.837952, 0.013268], [0.081704, 0.323589, 0.821062, 0.013268], [0.081704, 0.341403, 0.8397680000000001, 0.013268], [0.081704, 0.359218, 0.839664, 0.013268], [0.081704, 0.377033, 0.795919, 0.013268], [0.081704, 0.394848, 0.827611, 0.013268], [0.081704, 0.412662, 0.7641340000000001, 0.013268], [0.081704, 0.430477, 0.638855, 0.013268], [0.0931